villianStuff

Class Villian

  • java.lang.Object
    • villianStuff.Villian

  • public class Villian
extends java.lang.Object
    The class for the villains in the game, who must be defeated to progress to the next city or finish the game.
    The villains will have their primary attributes (those in the constructor) determined randomly within gameEnvironmentGuiRunTime.
    Author:
    cwe55, vjj14
